      "text": "等幅フォント",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772612554,
      "updated": 1772612554
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7ebca000000000047bbc8",
      "text": " すべての文字の幅を等しくしたフォント。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772612554,
      "updated": 1772612556
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7ebcb000000000047bbc9",
      "text": " 半角の英数字は、全角の漢字・仮名文字の半分の幅となる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772612556,
      "updated": 1772612556
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7ebcb000000000047bbca",
      "text": " 固定幅フォント。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772612556,
      "updated": 1772612556
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7ebe1000000000047bbcb",
